  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00330', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-112-606c6876', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '威廉遜迴旋（Williamsonturn）操船法之程序係於一般海況下得知人員落水後，向落水者一舷作大舵角轉 向，待艏向與原航向相差多少度數時，回舵並改朝另一舷作大舵角轉向，直至快要與原航向成相反方向 時，再穩舵慢行至可能落水位置附近？', '["240", "90", "60", "45"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "66336841947a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bcdd50686399", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "151", "s": "2005", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航行當值大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00331', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-112-606c6876', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關船舶迴旋圈上各距離之英文名詞，何者係指船舶以定速前進而用舵迴轉初期，船體將朝用舵的反 側偏離原航線所致之偏移距離？', '["Reach", "Transfer", "Advance", "Kick"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "66336841947a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bcdd50686399", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "151", "s": "2005", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航行當值大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00332', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-112-606c6876', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '某貨船於錨地拋錨時，大副回報：三節錨鏈入水，表示目前概已拋出多少噚（Fathom）的錨鏈長度位於水 面下？', '["45", "52.5", "75", "82.5"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "66336841947a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bcdd50686399", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "151", "s": "2005", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航行當值大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00333', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-112-606c6876', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '某研究船以12節航速，由深水區域駛進淺水區域，則該船之操控性受淺水效應的影響，下列敘述何者 正確？', '["迴旋能力增加", "舵力性能提升", "航向之穩定性提高", "船艉之航跡流減少"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "66336841947a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bcdd50686399", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "151", "s": "2005", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航行當值大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00334', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-112-606c6876', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '船舶固有的操縱性能包括：船舶追隨性、船舶定常迴轉性，及船舶航向穩定性；此三項特性會隨著船體方 塊係數（C ）的不同而有所變化。故對於C 大的船舶VLCC，其固有操縱性能相較於同噸位但C 小的貨 B B B 船，下列敘述何者正確？', '["追隨性和迴旋性較好，但航向穩定性則較差", "航向穩定性較好，但追隨性和迴旋性則較差", "追隨性較好，但迴旋性和航向穩定性則較差", "迴旋性較好，但追隨性和航向穩定性則較差"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "66336841947a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bcdd50686399", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "151", "s": "2005", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航行當值大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00335', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-112-606c6876', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列對船體運動六種自由度之中英文配對，何者正確？', '["左右橫移（Heaving）、左右艏艉搖（Yawing）", "前後縱移（Surging）、前後俯仰（Pitching）", "上下垂盪（Swaying）、左右橫搖（Rolling）", "前後縱移（Heaving）、左右艏艉搖（Pitching）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "66336841947a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bcdd50686399", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "151", "s": "2005", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航行當值大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
